        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "iJUZQ",
          "x": 0,
          "y": 55,
          "name": "ReaderMain",
          "width": 1160,
          "height": 845,
          "fill": "#0D0D0F",
          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "oxhtY",
              "x": 220,
              "y": 60,
              "name": "PageContent",
              "width": 720,
              "height": 780,
              "fill": "#00000000",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Kk4VJ",
                  "fill": "#FAFAFA",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "第三章　所有竞争都是失败的",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 20,
                  "fontWeight": "600"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "8tttA",
                  "fill": "#C4C4C8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "资本主义与竞争是对立的。资本主义建立在资本积累的基础之上，而在完全竞争的状态下，利润会被竞争消耗殆尽。然而，经济学家们的理论与商界领袖的实践之间存在根本性的矛盾。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "iRY1r",
                  "name": "hl1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FBBF2425",
                  "cornerRadius": 3,
                  "padding": [
                    2,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Jz5nu",
                      "fill": "#E8D5A3",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "如果你想创造并获取持久的价值，不要只是建立一个无差异的商品企业，要构建垄断。垄断企业可以负担得起思考长远利益的成本，而在竞争激烈的市场中生存的企业则不能。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "UxCNq",
                  "fill": "#C4C4C8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "从谷歌的角度来看这个问题。谷歌的广告收入远高于其他所有搜索引擎的总和。这是因为谷歌在搜索领域建立了真正的垄断，而不是与必应、雅虎在边际差异上竞争。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Pethv",
                  "name": "hl2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#60A5FA25",
                  "cornerRadius": 3,
                  "padding": [
                    2,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ZDajC",
                      "fill": "#A3C4E8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "垄断者可以通过把自己描述成在一个更大市场里竞争来隐藏自己的垄断地位；而处于激烈竞争中的企业则倾向于把自己描述为在一个小市场里的独一无二者。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "NKP8x",
                  "fill": "#C4C4C8",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "创业者的任务不是模仿竞争者，而是避免竞争。这意味着要在一个利基市场占据主导地位，然后从那里扩展，而不是在现有的大市场中寻找一席之地。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 15,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
